1304
01:23:34,399 --> 01:23:36,968
That's not... that's not fair.

1305
01:23:36,970 --> 01:23:40,304
- Why not?
- That's-that's not my sin.

1306
01:23:40,306 --> 01:23:42,807
Do you want to waste
these people's time?

1307
01:23:42,809 --> 01:23:43,975
I'm not.

1308
01:23:43,977 --> 01:23:46,345
No, these people
who got up here honestly

1309
01:23:46,347 --> 01:23:47,713
and were brave and...

