why do I have to be angry?

1334
01:24:47,950 --> 01:24:49,916
Just sit.

1335
01:24:49,918 --> 01:24:51,885
- Sit down.
- I'm not a dog!

1336
01:24:51,887 --> 01:24:53,987
- I know.
- And I don't think anyone is responsible for me,

1337
01:24:53,989 --> 01:24:55,556
so I don't see
how it's gonna help

1338
