coming from?

1341
01:25:01,131 --> 01:25:02,564
Because you're
making me angry!

1342
01:25:02,566 --> 01:25:04,800
There you go!
I want you to use that!

1343
01:25:04,802 --> 01:25:06,802
I'm not gonna pretend
I hate my father.

1344
01:25:06,804 --> 01:25:09,606
- I don't hate my father.
- Jared, you do.

1345
01:25:09,608 --> 01:25:12,175
