You're all crazy!

1346
01:25:12,177 --> 01:25:13,743
- Hey! I didn't...
- All of you!

1347
01:25:13,745 --> 01:25:15,579
Just... Jared.

1348
01:25:15,581 --> 01:25:18,616
You're in my chair!
There you go!

1349
01:25:18,618 --> 01:25:20,584
- Jared!
- I hate you!

1350
01:25:20,586 --> 01:25:24,289
- But how does that help?!
- Jared.

1351
01:25:24,291 --> 01:25:26,293
(CLEARS THROAT)

1352
01:25:29,429 --> 01:25:31,599
(PANTING)

1353
01:25:34,101 --> 01:25:35,469
VICTOR:
Jared!

1354
01:25:35,471 --> 01:25:38,672
Who's in the front office?

1355
01:25:38,674 --> 01:25:42,442
(PHONE RINGING)

1356
01:25:42,444 --> 01:25:45,981
Jared? Son, let's talk. Son?

1357
01:25:48,218 --> 01:25:50,952
Hey. Michael.

1358
01:25:50,954 --> 01:25:53,321
MICHAEL:
Hey, hey! Give it to me!

1359
01:25:53,323 --> 01:25:55,123
VICTOR:
Michael.

1360
01:25:55,125 --> 01:25:58,059
- I want my things and I want to go.
- Hey, Jared. Michael!

1361
01:25:58,061 --> 01:25:59,127
Hey!

1362
01:25:59,129 --> 01:26:00,230
(GRUNTING)

1363
01:26:00,232 --> 01:26:03,700
Hey! Michael!
Get out of the room!

1364
01:26:03,702 --> 01:26:05,903
Come here, son.

1365
01:26:07,838 --> 01:26:10,573
- Jared? Hey, hey. Hey, listen.
- (PANTING)

1366
01:26:10,575 --> 01:26:13,344
What you're having is
