if you don't open this door.

1428
01:28:23,493 --> 01:28:25,993
- There is no need for that. Listen, please.
- Jared!

1429
01:28:25,995 --> 01:28:28,463
- Let him go!
- (BRANDON GRUNTS)

1430
01:28:28,465 --> 01:28:31,968
- You all right, honey?
