I just... I think
it's more important for his...

1434
01:28:44,149 --> 01:28:46,483
development right now
that he...

1435
01:28:46,485 --> 01:28:48,152
- he would've stayed.
- NANCY: Don't even listen to him.

1436
01:28:48,154 --> 01:28:50,321
Get in the car.
Get in the car.

1437
01:28:50,323 --> 01:28:52,757
(NANCY PANTING)

1438
01:28:52,759 --> 01:28:54,426
VICTOR:
You're gonna ruin that child.

1439
01:28:54,428 --> 01:28:57,496
