1443
01:29:07,175 --> 01:29:10,176
No. I didn't think so.

1444
01:29:10,178 --> 01:29:12,348
(EXHALES):
Oh.

1445
01:29:13,449 --> 01:29:14,883
Shame on you!

1446
01:29:14,885 --> 01:29:16,083
