01:29:47,721 --> 01:29:49,488
WOMAN:
Can I help you?

1452
01:29:49,490 --> 01:29:51,991
JARED: Uh, I'm not sure
if I'm staying or going.

1453
01:29:51,993 --> 01:29:54,461
WOMAN: All right.
Well, let me know.

1454
01:30:05,007 --> 01:30:07,775
I talked to your father.

1455
01:30:07,777 --> 01:30:10,913
He wants you to go back.

1456
01:30:16,921 --> 01:30:19,187
I told him
we'll see him at home.

1457
01:30:19,189 --> 01:30:22,927
I told him you're not
going back.

1458
01:30:25,631 --> 01:30:28,632
You know that night...

1459
01:30:28,634 --> 01:30:32,269
