came to the house?

1460
01:30:32,271 --> 01:30:36,541
Those men decided what to do
with you, and I just...

1461
01:30:36,543 --> 01:30:40,948
I fell into line,
like I usually do.

1462
01:30:42,515 --> 01:30:45,116
They say sometimes
you got to hurt a child

1463
01:30:45,118 --> 01:30:47,286
in order to help them,
and that may be so

1464
01:30:47,288 --> 01:30:49,221
with some things, but...

1465
01:30:49,223 --> 01:30:52,959
a mother knows
when something isn't right.

1466
01:30:52,961 --> 01:30:56,696
And I knew in my bones...

1467
01:30:56,698 --> 01:30:59,402
this wasn't hurting to help.

1468
01:31:01,204 --> 01:31:05,976
I was just letting you down,
and I kept my mouth shut.

1469
01:31:09,647 --> 01:31:13,148
And I will always regret that.

1470
01:31:13,150 --> 01:31:15,485
♪ ♪

1471
01:31:15,487 --> 01:31:18,721
But I can do
a different thing now,

1472
01:31:18,723 --> 01:31:21,192
