of their Christian life...

1480
01:32:05,710 --> 01:32:07,543
to praise the Lord

1481
01:32:07,545 --> 01:32:11,314
and to help bring others
to his word.

1482
01:32:11,316 --> 01:32:14,485
It might be your neighbor,
it might be your friend,

1483
01:32:14,487 --> 01:32:17,220
it might be just a face
you only ever see at church.

1484
01:32:17,222 --> 01:32:20,458
They just turn up.

1485
01:32:20,460 --> 01:32:22,059
I will tell you something
that I know.

1486
01:32:22,061 --> 01:32:25,731
Just turning up to church
does not make you a Christian!

1487
01:32:25,733 --> 01:32:28,233
- Yes, sir.
- Amen.

1488
01:32:28,235 --> 01:32:31,104
MARSHALL: Study the Bible.
